source.name: GHDx - Global Health Data Exchange- Institute for health metrics and evaluation
source.description:
The GHDx, IHME's is a catalog of the world's health and demographic data. Use the GHDx to research population census data, surveys, registries, indicators and estimates, administrative health data, and financial data related to health.
- Search, browse, and find information about datasets. 
- Find out who can provide the data. 
 - Download IHME results and public-use datasets from other organizations.
